article.description: — Alex Morales and Elijah Ford each had 15 points as Wagner beat Fairfield 63-50 on Thursday.
article.headline: Morales, Ford each score 15 to carry Wagner past Fairfield
article.linkText: Morales, Ford each score 15 to carry Wagner past Fairfield
article.story: BRIDGEPORT, Conn. -- — Alex Morales and Elijah Ford each had 15 points as Wagner beat Fairfield 63-50 on Thursday. Raekwon Rogers added 11 points and Will Martinez had 10 points for Wagner (6-2). Caleb Green had 11 points for the Stags (8-5). Chris Maidoh added 10 points and Taj Benning had nine rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
